about.description:
My name is Dilam Anderson, a Systems Engineering student, a Full Stack developer with experience creating websites and desktop applications. I specialize in Java and JavaScript; I also have extensive experience in the area of ​​graphic design and editing.
Always in the constant search to polish my skills and continue to grow as a professional to present valuable contributions to the work group of which I am a part.
